847
00:52:31,880 --> 00:52:33,920
 nakon poroda je sedmi dan umrlo

848
00:52:33,920 --> 00:52:37,960
 djete je imala jednu kromosomsku grešku

849
00:52:37,960 --> 00:52:40,440
 i nije bilo pomoći

850
00:52:40,440 --> 00:52:42,640
 i djete je sedmi dan umrlo

851
00:52:42,640 --> 00:52:44,080
